    <name>Logseq</name>
    <summary>A local-first, non-linear, outliner notebook for organizing and sharing your personal knowledge base</summary>
    <content_rating type="oars-1.0" />

    <description>
        <p>Logseq is a platform for knowledge management and collaboration. It focuses on privacy, longevity, and user control.</p>
        <p>Your data are plain text files and we currently support both Markdown and Emacs Org mode (more to be added soon).</p>
    </description>

    <categories>
        <category>Office</category>
    </categories>
